<lb n="1"/>ṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g> svasti śrī jayābhyuda
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ya śālivāhana śaka 1615 ne
<lb n="3"/>yā śrīmukhanāma saṁvatsa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rada caitra śudha pāḍyada sō
<lb n="5" break="no"/>mavāra Aśvini nakṣatradalu
<lb n="6"/>siravārada staḷadali saṁjīva
<lb n="7"/>hanumaṁtadēvara nāmalagā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>viya jamadagni gōtrada veṁka
<lb n="9" break="no"/>panā maga gururāyanu sta(pa)
<lb n="10"/>māḍidanu maṁgaḷa mahā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g> śrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied>
